>DO YOU ACCEPT SCHOOL READINESS SUBSIDIZED CHILD CARE?</h2>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">No.</div>\n<h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\">DO YOU ACCEPT ANY TYPES OF SCHOLARSHIPS?</h2>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">Yes.  We accept the McKay Scholarship, the Step Up For Students Scholarship, and the Personal Learning Scholarship.</div>\n<h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\">HOW DO I SCHEDULE A TOUR?</h2>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">Please call  (321) 268-3365.  We will put you in touch with the appropriate staff member for the grade you are looking for.</div>\n<h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\">HOW CAN I CONTACT YOU?</h2>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">Please call (321) 268-3365 or e-mail us at LFMA@cfl.rr.com.</div>','Common Questions','','publish','closed','closed','','common-questions','','','2016-01-19 18:32:03','2016-01-19 18:32:03','',0,'http://DB26474D-8FC4-4244-95F2-13DBE57BE551',0,'page','',0),(418,1,'2016-03-03 14:13:09','2016-03-03 14:13:09','[contact-form][contact-field label=\'Name\' type=\'name\' required=\'1\'/][contact-field label=\'Email\' type=\'email\' required=\'1\'/][contact-field label=\'Testimonial\' type=\'textarea\' required=\'1\'/][/contact-form]','Testimonials','','publish','closed','closed','','testimonials','','','2016-03-03 14:13:09','2016-03-03 14:13:09','',0,'http://BA3FA7F9-8B30-419B-9608-A4FA1C55498A',0,'page','',0),(419,1,'2016-05-24 18:20:23','2016-05-24 18:20:23','Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start writing!','Hello world!','','publish','open','open','','hello-world-3','','','2016-05-24 18:20:23','2016-05-24 18:20:23','',0,'http://6D99B220-2921-4C43-A583-27212E9DFA54',0,'post','',1),(420,1,'2016-05-24 18:20:49','2016-05-24 18:20:49','','LP Profile','','publish','closed','closed','','lp-profile-2','','','2016-05-24 18:20:49','2016-05-24 18:20:49','',0,'http://9F5E7D07-85D8-4AEB-9D2F-DBC7E5BB83BF',0,'page','',0),(421,1,'2016-05-24 18:20:49','2016-05-24 18:20:49','','LP Courses','','publish','closed','closed','','lp-